event.logging

Class BaseObjectOutcome

  • java.lang.Object
    • event.logging.BaseObjectOutcome
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventAction, HasOutcome
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CreateEventAction, DeleteEventAction, ViewEventAction

    public abstract class BaseObjectOutcome
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventAction, HasOutcome
    Contains an item of data, e.g. a file, document, etc, and describes the outcome of the event as well as providing for additional event data that does not fit into the item of data element.

    Java class for BaseObjectOutcome complex type.
